    "causal_summary": "Phase A (diagnostic-only `/doctor:code-graph`) shipped in `005-code-graph/005-doctor-diagnostic-command-phase-a/`, gated Phase B behind four artifacts from research packet `006-code-graph-resilience-research`. All four artifacts are now in place: a 28-query gold battery (`assets/code-graph-gold-queries.json`), a 3-state staleness model (`assets/staleness-model.md`), three recovery procedures (`assets/recovery-playbook.md`), and 3-tier exclude-rule confidence (`assets/exclude-rule-confidence.json`). Phase B wires them into an apply-mode workflow that runs the gold battery as a pre/post-flight verification gate, executes the appropriate recovery procedure based on staleness state, and rolls back if verification fails.",
